REQUIREMENTS:
 
 - FUSE 2.* (tested with FUSE 2.3 and newer) (http://fuse.sourceforge.net)
 - fuse-python (http://fuse.sourceforge.net/wiki/index.php/FusePython)
 - In general, Python 2.4 or newer. May run with older versions, its only tested with 2.4

INSTALLATION:

The best way to install this module is to run the setup script
provided with this module.

'sudo python setup.py install'

Will install the required files. 'sudo' is required since the files
would be install in system dierctories.
